## Rollout Phases

### Phase 1 — Now (TASK_023)
- Create `listing_fault_outcomes` table
- Auto-populate a row for every fault detected, `confirmed=NULL`
- Ensures data accumulates from day one

### Phase 2 — Next month
- Normalise fault_type vocabulary
- Add fault normalisation step to detection worker
- Clean up existing `detected_faults` records

### Phase 3 — When pipeline is stable (~1 month)
- DVSA MOT data ingestion
- Populate `mot_failure_priors`
- Build nightly `fault_probability_cache` job

### Phase 4 — When cache is populated
- Upgrade Detection Step 3 to query `fault_probability_cache`
- Feed statistical priors into AI prompt
- Measure confidence score uplift

### Phase 5 — When user feedback exists
- Wire user feedback to update `confirmed` field on `listing_fault_outcomes`
- Confirmed observations start updating posteriors
- Model becomes self-improving
